properties.id: The ID of the inventory level.

properties.stocked_quantity: The stocked quantity of the inventory level
properties.reserved_quantity: The reserved quantity of the inventory level
properties.incoming_quantity: The incoming quantity of the inventory level
properties.metadata: Holds custom data in key-value pairs.
properties.available_quantity: The available quantity of the inventory level

properties.line_item_id: The ID of the reservation item's line item.
properties.allow_backorder: Whether the underlying item can still be ordered despite the reserved quantity.
properties.location_id: The ID of the location that the quantity is reserved from. When used with the [Stock Location Module](https://docs.medusajs.com/resources/commerce-modules/stock-location), the ID will be a `StockLocation`'s ID.
properties.external_id: The external ID of the reservation item. Can store an ID from a third-party system.
properties.description: The description of the reservation item
properties.created_by: The ID of the user that created the reservation item.
properties.metadata: Holds custom data in key-value pairs.
